VCS-Git: git://github.com/ev3dev-dpkg/polystrap.git
VCS-Browser: https://github.com/ev3dev-dpkg/polystrap.git

Package: polystrap
Architecture: all
Depends: qemu-user (>= 1.0), multistrap, proot, ${misc:Depends}
Description: multistrap wrapper to build foreign rootfs
 This package allows one to build a foreign debian rootfs using qemu user mode
 emulation, multistrap and proot without the need of superuser priviliges.
